.call-out.call-out--long
  .call-out__image(style="background-image: url('/images/consumers/banner.jpg')")
    .call-out__image__content
      h1.h3-like.call-out__title Consumers
  .call-out__list-container.js-dropdown
    button.call-out__mobile-list.js-dropdown-button.for-tablet Consumers
    ul.call-out__list.js-dropdown-content
      li
        a(href="/transformation-journey.html") Transformation Journey
      li
        a(href="/harm-reduction.html") Harm Reduction
      li.is-active
        a(href="/consumers.html") Consumers
  .call-out__content.container-lg
    .call-out__content__text
      h2 We are on a mission to meet the evolving preferences of adult tobacco consumers by providing a range of products, each with unique characteristics designed to meet consumer preferences and demand. Our mission is epitomized by our operating companies’ brands, which provide a portfolio of products designed to fit the modern-day adult tobacco consumer – delivering choice, convenience and consideration.
    .call-out__content__image(style="background-image: url('/images/consumers/image-1.jpg')")

article.block-image-and-text.mobile-offset-top-and-bottom-desktop
  .container-lg
    .row.align-items-center
      .col-lg-6.image-container
        img(src="/images/consumers/image-2.jpg" srcset="/images/consumers/image-2@2x.jpg 2x" alt="")
      .col-lg-6.text-container
        h2.h3-like Meeting Evolving Expectations
        .border-left
          p Adult tobacco consumers’ evolving expectations are driven by a change in societal norms and behavior, and the way people think about the enjoyment of tobacco and nicotine products. Our suite of brands and product offerings are designed to meet adult tobacco consumers where they want us to be.

article.block-image-and-text.block-offset-top-and-bottom
  .container-lg
    .row.align-items-center
      .col-lg-6.image-container.order-lg-2
        img(src="/images/consumers/image-3.jpg" srcset="/images/consumers/image-3@2x.jpg 2x" alt="")
      .col-lg-6.text-container.order-lg-1
        .border-left
          ul.ul-like.li-full
            li Adult consumers are at the core of everything we do, and meeting consumer preferences drives our product-development process. We are dedicated to developing and responsibly marketing products that provide a range of enjoyable options for a diverse range of experiences and occasions.
            li Our product portfolio responds to these tastes by providing a range of products, some of which produce less waste and no smoke, compared to combustibles. This allows adult consumers who choose to use tobacco or nicotine products to enjoy them while remaining considerate of the preferences of those around them.
            li We are excited for the future of our industry and to define the path that effects change in our society.
